The SyntaxDiagramMojo can be configured like this:

<plugins>
  <plugin>
    <groupId>de.banapple.maven</groupId>
    <artifactId>antlr-maven-plugin</artifactId>
    <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
    <configuration>
      <grammarFile>src/main/antlr/mygrammar.g</grammarFile>
    </configuration>
  </plugin>
</plugins>

You will need an antlrworks artifact in your maven repository.
I have not found any repository which includes this artifact, so
you will have to install it yourself. 
The plugin uses org.antlr:antlrworks:1.4.3
